          <h2>Why Choose CallBrownsPainting.com for Daphne Projects</h2>
          
          <div class="specialties-grid">
            <div class="specialty-item">
              <h3>Eastern Shore Expertise</h3>
              <p>
                We understand the unique challenges of painting in Daphne's Eastern Shore climate. 
                High humidity and coastal weather require specialized techniques and materials.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="specialty-item">
              <h3>Local Knowledge</h3>
              <p>
                Based in Brewton, we're familiar with Daphne's neighborhoods, architectural styles, 
                and local regulations. We know what works best for Eastern Shore properties.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="specialty-item">
              <h3>Quality Materials</h3>
              <p>
                We use premium paints and materials specifically chosen for Daphne's climate. 
                Humidity-resistant paints prevent peeling and mold growth.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="specialty-item">
              <h3>Reliable Service</h3>
              <p>
                Professional communication, on-time completion, and quality workmanship. 
                We're committed to your satisfaction on every Daphne project.
              </p>
            </div>
